title: Jason of Star Command - {Complete Series} DVDrip
description:
Jason of Star Command

A spinoff of another Filmation live action show called "Space Academy". Star Command's job was to protect the innocent from the bad guys, most notably Jason's archenemy, the one-eyed Dragos.Its first season, a segment of Tarzan and the Super 7 was done in the style of the movie serials of the past, telling a single overall story with sixteen "chapters" of approximately fifteen minutes' length, each ending in a cliffhanger. The second season was a stand-alone, half-hour series.
